Init ( generate a tsconfig.json which specify the compiler options )
    npx --package typescript tsc --init

Compile 
npx --package typescript tsc -w
or
npx --package typescript tsc

type inference when using typescript 

any vs unknown 

if you don't know what type it will be, try using unknown instead of any


arrays 

object

type aliases

function type 

    optional parameters 

